<p>â€” [â€¦] As for Mari, there is a scene where she has a conversation with Shinji after he parts from Misato. She imitates Asukaâ€™s manner of speaking there, right? Afterwards, at the climax of the battle where Unit-01 grows wings, she is staring at it from a distanceâ€¦</p>
<p><code>Higuchi:</code> If I had to say, Iâ€™d say she was like a female version of Kaworu.</p>
